{"tid":2258120,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"Joseph Gordon撐香港，佢哋首英詩你又讀咗未？","createTime":"2020-10-25T18:27:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T16:23:14.000Z","uid":17335,"like":141,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"d9ba3232252fac3cf8ea0729bc76d7c39953b966","tid":2258120,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T18:27:33.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\">念念「不眠」，心在「香港」：淺談詩歌 &ldquo;Hong Kong Never Sleeps&rdquo;</p><br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1*lrIDPOrFO5O5BEH802T6Ww.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F1400%2F1%2AlrIDPOrFO5O5BEH802T6Ww.jpeg&h=4ea747f3&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n著名荷里活影星祖瑟夫&middot;哥頓-利域（Joseph Gordon-Levitt）早前曾向網民徵集拍有香港風景的相片，最近，他又廣邀網民到其創辦的網上媒體平台HitRecord朗誦英詩。<br />\n<br />\n這首詩由Matt Conley（HitRecord的社群總監）所寫，詩歌的名字叫做〈不眠香港〉（Hong Kong Never Sleeps），不少媒體在報道時，都強調這詩讚揚香港人是「自由鬥士」（Freedom Fighters）。<br />\n<br />\n這首詩並不難讀，我們從詩歌中得到鼓舞之餘，也可由以下兩個角度欣賞這首作品。<br />\n<br />\n一、 詩歌如何描寫香港景物？<br />\n<br />\n不少外國人對香港的印象都流於刻板（例如維多利亞海港與舊帆船、太平山上俯瞰高樓大廈），這首詩也有一些詩句未能免俗 &mdash; &mdash; 例如說香港是「東方的美人」（A beauty in the orient）。<br />\n但在形容香港的外觀上，也頗見心思。例如第四段寫道：「我們可以一直觀看/這個屬於我們所有人的家園/日子清明的時候/青天藍海之間/港口與群山便會構成一頁頁風景」。<br />\n<br />\n詩人特意點出「觀看」（see），而且還說這種觀看是可以一直維持到永遠，既肯定美景常在，也呼應了Hong Kong Never Sleeps這主題。同時，亦使人不禁要問：「是誰令青山也變？」<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/0*bvdlUvp_dqK6ASIU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F1400%2F0%2AbvdlUvp_dqK6ASIU&h=b3bf979a&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n二、 詩中如何表現香港的「精神」？<br />\n<br />\n除了外在的觀看，詩人不忘頌揚香港的內在價值。第二段寫道「香港本身自成一個世界」（a world of its own）/即使面對未知的路/我們就在這土地上/寫下屬於自己的歷史/而且團結一致，從不孤單」。<br />\n<br />\n在第三段，詩人提到「雨的淚水」、「街上的人」這些畫面相信大家都不會陌生。而且，「自由鬥士」即使一臉痛苦，他們的聲音仍然會被聽見、傳播四方。<br />\n<br />\n2020年將成過去，亦意味着21世紀亦過了五分之一，但香港在世界上的位置已再不一樣，我們看見各地的街道上都踏着相似的腳步，追逐着相同的目標。與此同時，香港對我們來說也不再一樣。如今，即使你我難免疲倦，現在還不是閉目待斃的時候 &mdash; &mdash;<br />\n<br />\n香港不眠<br />\n因為我們仍然有夢<br />\n因為我們會在醒着時把它們好好實現<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/0*3V9RIgju7Lv652lB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F1400%2F0%2A3V9RIgju7Lv652lB.jpg&h=c2356875&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Hong Kong Never Sleeps&rdquo; Matt Conley<br />\nHong Kong, she never sleeps<br />\nA beauty in the orient<br />\nA smiling dragon that breathes<br />\nShe is fire on water<br />\nA city of spirited souls and passing ships<br />\nHong Kong, a world of its own<br />\nWhere we write our own history<br />\nUpon pathways unknown,<br />\nBut never alone<br />\nWe forever stand as one<br />\nHong Kong, weeping tears of rain<br />\nBringing together people in the streets<br />\nFreedom fighters<br />\nWith faces of pain<br />\nAnd voices that will be heard<br />\nHong Kong, a home to us all<br />\nWith layers of landscapes, harbors and hills<br />\nBetween blue skies and blue seas<br />\nOn clear days<br />\nYou can see forever<br />\nHong Kong, our sacred city<br />\nWalking and talking through avenues<br />\nSo full of life<br />\nThe place we settle in to sleep<br />\nAnd fill with dreams in the night<br />\n<br />\n想睇更多文藝嘢，歡迎Follow德尼思化：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nIG <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/delis.ver/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdelis.ver%2F&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oAp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=f20014a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/delis.ver/</a><br />\nFB <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Delisver.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDelisver.hk%2F&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oAp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=d563c48d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Delisver.hk/</a><br />\nMedium <a href=\"http://bit.ly/36HvepQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F36HvepQ&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oAp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=cc784009\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/36HvepQ</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf847a1a2be3fc7ab480a52003af78f140964ff","tid":2258120,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T18:28:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5cd8782debb5555ee2787e88d8b6942f01f39dd8","tid":2258120,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baf847a1a2be3fc7ab480a52003af78f140964ff","tid":2258120,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T18:28:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T18:29:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝巴打撐場"},{"pid":"3f464f6ee90be15fd5a9bade19385e66e7c1fc9e","tid":2258120,"uid":17335,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T18:31:14.000Z","msg":"排版問題，分返首英詩嘅段落先<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Hong Kong Never Sleeps&rdquo; Matt Conley<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong, she never sleeps<br />\nA beauty in the orient<br />\nA smiling dragon that breathes<br />\nShe is fire on water<br />\nA city of spirited souls and passing ships<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong, a world of its own<br />\nWhere we write our own history<br />\nUpon pathways unknown,<br />\nBut never alone<br />\nWe forever stand as one<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong, weeping tears of rain<br />\nBringing together people in the streets<br />\nFreedom fighters<br />\nWith faces of pain<br />\nAnd voices that will be heard<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong, a home to us all<br />\nWith layers of landscapes, harbors and hills<br />\nBetween blue skies and blue seas<br />\nOn clear days<br />\nYou can see forever<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong, our sacred city<br />\nWalking and talking through avenues<br />\nSo full of life<br />\nThe place we settle in to sleep<br />\nAnd fill with dreams in the night"},{"pid":"d33f550eb5393ec3fcb2f3ee080f428149e877a3","tid":2258120,"uid":12864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T18:47:07.000Z","msg":"JGL<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb1b7f432f661a5e68153ec9f8ec4eac1aa42d93","tid":2258120,"uid":122988,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T18:48:35.000Z","msg":"佢套the trial of chicago 7係netflix上左 一定要睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d65f4771c649b47ed616ff73e47f893e8238c66","tid":2258120,"uid":188907,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T18:49:26.000Z","msg":"好撚中意佢"},{"pid":"054d7846ef3ab86b2c15fc8274aa0f7e556e04d6","tid":2258120,"uid":17335,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb1b7f432f661a5e68153ec9f8ec4eac1aa42d93","tid":2258120,"uid":122988,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T18:48:35.000Z","msg":"佢套the trial of chicago 7係netflix上左 一定要睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T18:58:04.000Z","msg":"香港人必睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打識貨"},{"pid":"c54efc2d0359607c26f7486edbe6e5ed1f149300","tid":2258120,"uid":17335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8d65f4771c649b47ed616ff73e47f893e8238c66","tid":2258120,"uid":188907,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T18:49:26.00